text: La Compagnie is a French airline based at Orly Airport in Paris. The airlines' aircraft have only business class seats. ==History== La Compagnie was founded as DreamJet in 2013. By the time the airline operated its first scheduled flight on 21 July 2014, it had been renamed as La Compagnie. Category:Airlines of France Category:2013 establishments in France
title: La Compagnie
